            <div class="copy">
                <p>
                    Arnold Porter raised his hands, looked up to the sky and joined in song with other church members around him. ‚ÄúThe Lord called me here to this congregation in 2013. I love it here and I like that I can come here or be a part of it at home,‚Äù he said. 
                    <br>
<br/>
Thanks to the use of technology, churches like World Changers International are able to enter the hearts and homes of thousands of people across the world. 
<br>
<br/>
The number of people at World Changers International Church in the Bronx has gotten smaller over the years, however, the congregation isn‚Äôt shrinking. The use of technology has allowed the church to expand and allowed more members to join the church. Members of all ages have joined services from the comfort of their homes as televangelism takes on new forms. 

</p>
            </div>
            <img src="img/chart.png" alt="chart" display="none" margin="none" width="100%">


     
            <div class="cap">
                <p> Margins? We don't need no stinkin' margins. Change the style of your captions to denote a difference in content. </p>
