                        Apps are also available for members to request prayers, read scriptures, check upcoming church events and give money to the church. A year ago, the church began a podcast, allowing listeners to access more of Dollar‚Äôs lessons. 
<br>
<br/>
Technology has created new opportunities for members to attend this particular church, access sermons, and connect with other members online. 
